character_models.name: Leonardo Anime XL
character_models.description: A new high-speed Anime-focused model that excels at a range of anime, illustrative, and CG styles.

character_models.name: Leonardo Lightning XL
character_models.description: Our new high-speed generalist image gen model. Great at everything from photorealism to painterly styles.

character_models.name: Leonardo Vision XL
character_models.description: A versatile model that excels at realism and photography. Better results with longer prompts.

character_models.name: Leonardo Diffusion XL
character_models.description: The next phase of the core Leonardo model. Stunning outputs, even with short prompts.

character_models.name: 3D Animation Style
character_models.description: Great at 3D film vibes, capable of complex scenes with rich color. Storyboard time!

character_models.name: DreamShaper v7
character_models.description: Lykon is back with another update. This model is great at a range of different styles.

character_models.name: Cute Characters
character_models.description: Create cute and charming game characters, perfect for adding some whimsy to your game design. Be sure to include the word "character" in your prompts for best results.

character_models.name: Spirit Creatures
character_models.description: From whimsical fairy-like beings to mythical creatures, create unique cute spirit characters.

character_models.name: Cute Animal Characters
character_models.description: Perfect for creating adorable and cute animal characters - loveable and playful designs.

additional_models.name: Chest Armor
additional_models.description: Create all sorts of chest armor with this model in a consistent style but with wide thematic range.

additional_models.name: Magic Potions
additional_models.description: A great model for creating incredible semi-realistic magic potions. Try appending "intricately detailed, 3d vray render" to your prompt.

additional_models.name: Magic Items
additional_models.description: Create a wide range of magical items like weapons, shields, boots, books. Very versatile.

additional_models.name: Character Portraits
additional_models.description: A model that's for creating awesome RPG characters of varying classes in a consistent style.

additional_models.name: Amulets
additional_models.description: Create unique and intricate amulets, jewellery and more. Try loading up the prompt terms to steer it in interesting directions.

additional_models.name: Isometric Scifi Buildings
additional_models.description: Great at creating scifi buildings of varying themes. Append the word isometric to your prompt to ensure an isometric view. "3d vray render" also helps steer the generation well.

additional_models.name: Isometric Fantasy
additional_models.description: Create all sorts of isometric fantasy environments. Try appending "3d vray render, isometric" and using a guidance scale of 6. For the negative prompt, try "unclear, harsh, oversaturated, soft, blurry".

additional_models.name: Shields
additional_models.description: Create a variety of impressively varied and detailed shield designs. Allows for an incredible range of material types.

additional_models.name: Crystal Deposits Alternate
additional_models.description: An alternative crystal deposits model that gives a slightly more realistic feel with its creations. Try using "object" and "3d vray render" in your prompts.

additional_models.name: Isometric Asteroid Tiles
additional_models.description: A model for creating isometric asteroid environment tiles. Try appending "3d vray render, unreal engine, beautiful, intricately detailed, trending on artstation, 8k" to your prompt.

additional_models.name: Leonardo Signature
additional_models.description: The core model of the Leonardo platform. An extremely powerful and diverse finetune which is highly effective for a wide range of uses.
